dct_description_sm: This tabular data, prepared by Data You Can Use, presents population data for Asian, Black, Latinx/Hispanic and white residents by census tract for the City of Milwaukee from 2010-2016. The data is sourced from the 2010 Decennial Census Table PCT1, 2012-1026 American Community Survey 5-Year Estimate, and utilizes 2010 Census tracts. For more information, please visit Data You Can Use.
